data.name: xrLabel12.Scripts.OnBeforePrint
data.value:
Private Sub OnBeforePrint(ByVal sender As Object, ByVal e As System.Drawing.Printing.PrintEventArgs) 'Get the current value of the "Fax" data column Dim _StrCom as string = GetCurrentColumnValue("communication").ToString() Dim _Char as char Dim _i as integer 'Check if the value is null, then cancel the printing xrLabel12.text = "+ + +" for _i = 0 to _StrCom.Length - 1 _char = _strCom.chars(_i) xrLabel12.text = xrLabel12.text & " " & _char if _i = 2 then xrLabel12.text = xrLabel12.text & " /" end if if _i = 6 then xrLabel12.text = xrLabel12.text & " /" end if Next xrLabel12.text = xrLabel12.text & " + + +"
End Sub
